Name: teat
Subject: teat
HtmlBody:
First and foremost, I am wishing you and your families well during this crazy time. To the veterans, I know career transition under regular conditions is stressful, I can only imagine what many of you are going through right now.

Like many other organizations, Elite Meet has had to change the way we do business (physical events are postponed indefinitely at this point). In their absence, we have shifted our resources towards digitizing the EM network on some new software so you all have 24/7 access no matter what’s going on in the world.


We are calling this new product, “Elite Meet Connect” (EM Connect for short) and it will be an online networking platform where EM members will be able to directly connect with the EM professional & veteran network. Additionally there will be webinars, e-courses, and other valuable transition resources at member’s disposal. Meg Thatford & her team have already built out the back end structure and will be adding EM members soon.


EM Connect will serve as EM’s primary resource for networking until in-person events resume. And even after they resume, we may find that EM Connect is the preferred option. We will just have to wait and see.

Stay tuned for updates in the coming weeks about EM Connect. Feel free to reach out to me via email if you have any questions. john@elitemeet.us
 

Thank you for your continued support.
 

-John

Name: Airtable opt-in list
Subject: Airtable opt-in list
HtmlBody:
Good Afternoon Everyone

Airtable is a digital database to be able to file and organize different tasks and information. EM is using it to be able to promote you and your skill sets, that everyone can use, to share information with potential employers or just have the ability to reach out to any fellow EM member.  Also, as of now there are select number of employers that are looking at this base, and more will have access in the near future to be able to farm from, so be professional!


I’d like to say that there won’t be any hiccups on my end, as far as managing the influx of members submitting forms, but only time will tell. My short term goal at this point, once a majority have filled this form out, is to send out a mass Link, or a personal link, to give you access to this information that you and other members have supplied. 

 

As of now, there are a little over 100 members that have submitted this form, but there are a few additions and changes. If you are one of those people, please feel free to text, email, call or DM me and I will happily check that out and make any updates to your form if need be, or you can submit a new form and I’ll be able to use the new one to update the old one. 

 

Please follow the link that below.  If there are any issues, again, feel free to contact me.

 

https://airtable.com/shrs8ahGtQudaNYqY

 

Nick Blough

Airtable program manager 

Nicholas.blough@elitemeet.us

(217)971-9317

Name: Airtable Opt-in List
Subject: Airtable Opt-in List
HtmlBody:
Good Afternoon Everyone,

My name is Nick Blough.  I am a currently helping EM with their Digital platform. If you're on Slack you have probably seen a couple of my posts about Airtable. What it is, is a digital database to be able to file and organize different tasks and information. By means of searching, sorting, and filtering the database. It will make finding the right member for the right job that much easier for employers.  EM is using it to be able to promote you and your skill sets, to share contact and career interest information with potential employers. Currently there are select number of employers that are looking at this base, and actively persuing job seeking Veterans, and more will have access in the near future!

 

As of now, there are a little over 100 members that have submitted this form, but there are a few additions and changes. If you are one of those 100+, please feel free to email me and I will happily check that out and make any updates to your form if need be, or you can submit a new form and I’ll be able to use the new one to update the old one. 

To reiterate, this is an Opt-in list. Do not feel obligated to fill this form out if you do not want your information shared.

 

Please follow the link below.  If there are any issues, please feel free to contact me.

 

https://airtable.com/shrs8ahGtQudaNYqY

Kind Regards,

 

Nick Blough/SEAL

Airtable program manager 

Nicholas.blough@elitemeet.us

(217)971-9317
